title: Hour 3 – Covino and Rich Guest Host
itunes:title: Hour 3 – Covino and Rich Guest Host
description:
Covino and Rich fill in for Dan Patrick and the crew and take some calls before getting into the suspension of Mr. Phone in pocket while sliding into 3rd base’s suspension. Do the Dodgers need to start worrying about their pitching staff?
